{
  "2302120": {
    "name": "Infinitum: The Backrooms Story",
    "steam_appid": 2302120,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/ec5d3ebd029a63eaa634b06c2415bb1b.webp?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=26 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Infinitum》拥有一个具有多个结局的独特故事，你所做的每一个选择都很重要。它以重新想象的密室宇宙为背景，提供新鲜、恐怖的恐怖体验。这不仅仅是另一款你“在密室醒来”并试图逃跑的游戏。你的决定决定了你在游戏中的结果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/0fea607315dba3d9e39f583d4093369c.poster.avif?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/0fea607315dba3d9e39f583d4093369c.webm?t=1768242485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/0fea607315dba3d9e39f583d4093369c.mp4?t=1768242485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/9c699cf5138ba4c4483e4cd411b66030.webp?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=26 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/abb2a28d488cb6d588bfaf87c46c420d.webp?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=26 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开放世界的非线性游戏玩法提供了多种在关卡之间移动的方式，让您可以选择自己想要的《INFINITUM》游戏方式。您可以欣赏 37 层的美景，也可以迷失在 33 层的无限购物中心中——如果您愿意的话。请务必仔细聆听，因为您永远不知道谁或什么可能潜伏在拐角处。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/8e0f9bd988d8bb48630c8a8d5f4ec1d2.poster.avif?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/8e0f9bd988d8bb48630c8a8d5f4ec1d2.webm?t=1768242485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/8e0f9bd988d8bb48630c8a8d5f4ec1d2.mp4?t=1768242485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/9c699cf5138ba4c4483e4cd411b66030.webp?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=26 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/44ef6c2dbaa1135e0e5025082aba2e25.webp?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=26 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Infinitum 拥有许多有助于玩家体验的游戏机制和功能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/574ea4318565577a3c5b70ca6db5c115.webp?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=26 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多人投票系统确保玩家共同做出决定，例如前往特定级别或开始任务。每个玩家都必须投票“是”或“否”才能继续前进，并且需要集体协议。请注意，您只有几秒钟的时间做出决定，否则您的投票将被自动拒绝。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/aecd640e3109e3d36ab12d3baa35869b.poster.avif?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/aecd640e3109e3d36ab12d3baa35869b.webm?t=1768242485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/aecd640e3109e3d36ab12d3baa35869b.mp4?t=1768242485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/c499ec929a2855ef67248ed35d02ea41.webp?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=26 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地堡是你的个人安全屋，也是保存你进度的唯一地方。在里面，你可以储存、制作和建造物品来帮助你的旅程。您还可以为您的掩体命名并自定义灯光颜色，使其感觉更加个性化和讨人喜欢。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/71d222f7616821faf70930f6fe904fdf.poster.avif?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/71d222f7616821faf70930f6fe904fdf.webm?t=1768242485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/71d222f7616821faf70930f6fe904fdf.mp4?t=1768242485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/e148d020b80f758d0b90f3118a7f6912.webp?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=26 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要到达前哨站，您必须从地堡穿过隧道。到达那里后，您可以与 NPC 互动、完成任务并做出推动故事发展的关键决定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/898f5880c93b6aad35dd4375988740a4.webp?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=26 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Infinitum 建立在基于图块的生成系统之上，每次进入关卡时都会产生新鲜的体验。每个级别都有预建的房间，这些房间具有随机属性，例如墙壁、物品和实体。这些房间随机且无限地出现。这种不可预测性是《Infinitum》的精髓，保证每次游戏都感觉像是一次新的冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/19873db4da9ef92ac7f48068f9c4f772.poster.avif?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/19873db4da9ef92ac7f48068f9c4f772.webm?t=1768242485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/19873db4da9ef92ac7f48068f9c4f772.mp4?t=1768242485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/f2e317f45f13ab8bad9cae34f480e4ab.webp?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=26 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了在游戏中生存，你必须吃喝来维持体力。如果你的耐力耗尽，你的角色将无法冲刺，如果一个实体开始追你，你就更难逃脱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/445d5d5d7c7df4324b28cc5040dfabf0.poster.avif?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/445d5d5d7c7df4324b28cc5040dfabf0.webm?t=1768242485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/445d5d5d7c7df4324b28cc5040dfabf0.mp4?t=1768242485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/87d92306a8ca318189a761967145969a.webp?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=26 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色定制在游戏中发挥着重要作用。通过完成任务和成就，您将能够购买各种危险品套装颜色和型号、徽章和其他配件来个性化您的角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/f7a7eb5ce39404f8b82c317ef6d0d196.poster.avif?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/f7a7eb5ce39404f8b82c317ef6d0d196.webm?t=1768242485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/f7a7eb5ce39404f8b82c317ef6d0d196.mp4?t=1768242485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/d30decd4364e1d4b2a6f2fd71ea1af7f.webp?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=26 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论您想在没有跳跃恐惧的情况下玩游戏、正常地玩游戏、玩硬核游戏还是在没有实体的情况下进行探索，Infinitum 都可以通过各种游戏模式、自定义世界和深入的设置来满足您的需求。<strong>   </strong><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/a8895c8532d0e1ea73a8a111a2848b91.webp?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=26 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果这还不能说服你，你还可以收养肥猫，它们将永远呆在你的地堡里。 （那是我们的金票！）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/9c699cf5138ba4c4483e4cd411b66030.webp?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=26 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/e747173ee889ca703160af7429c22222.webp?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=26 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Infinitum 采用最新的虚幻引擎 5 技术构建，可提供令人印象深刻的图形。然而，我们知道并不是每个人都拥有高端计算机，因此我们引入了性能模式。此选项会降低图形质量，让低端电脑的玩家可以流畅地享受游戏。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/0d84fe37a33d1eace5f4ffbc182e6542.poster.avif?t=1768242485\" width=620 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/0d84fe37a33d1eace5f4ffbc182e6542.webm?t=1768242485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302120/extras/0d84fe37a33d1eace5f4ffbc182e6542.mp4?t=1768242485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个周日都会更新帖子。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 阿拉伯语, 保加利亚语, 捷克语, 丹麦语, 荷兰语, 芬兰语, 希腊语, 匈牙利语, 印度尼西亚语, 日语, 韩语, 挪威语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 罗马尼亚语, 俄语, 简体中文, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 瑞典语, 泰语, 繁体中文, 土耳其语, 乌克兰语, 越南语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
